ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of January, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition for Writs of Mandamus, Habeas Corpus, Injunctive, Prohibition and/or Extraordinary Relief’ is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
